This is a trending photo of two of the most popular actors in Nigeria innocently performing their work on an unnamed movie set. Social media users have been sharing a picture of Richard Mofe Damijo, RMD locking lips with a married actress and mother of three, Omoni Oboli. Although, some people have been reading meanings to the undated image, it has been clarified as a set photo. Omoni, a graduate of the University of Ibadan is one of the few Nigerian actresses who has successfully managed her acting career with her marriage. RMD on the other hand is an elderly man who is well sought after by young ladies and women due to his good looks. Source